The impact of dietary risk factors on the burden of non-communicable diseases in 
Ethiopia: findings from the Global Burden of Disease study 2013.

Melaku YA(1)(2), Temesgen AM(3), Deribew A(4)(5)(6), Tessema GA(7)(8), Deribe 
K(9)(10)(11), Sahle BW(12)(13), Abera SF(12)(14), Bekele T(15), Lemma F(11), 
Amare AT(16)(17)(18), Seid O(12), Endris K(12), Hiruye A(11), Worku A(19), Adams 
