Minimal improvements in the global burden of skin disease from 1990 to 2013.

Mounessa J(1), Braunberger T(2), Dunnick CA(3), Dellavalle RP(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Dermatology, University of Colorado Anschutz Medical Campus, 
