Survival and Development of Hermetia illucens (Diptera: Stratiomyidae): A 
Biodegradation Agent of Organic Waste.

[Article in English, Spanish; Abstract available in Spanish from the publisher]

Clariza Samayoa A(1), Chen WT(1), Hwang SY(2).

Author information:
(1)Department of Entomology, National Chung Hsing University, Taichung, Taiwan 
402 (anaclariza@gmail.com; miss184184@gmail.com; oleander@dragon.nchu.edu.tw).
(2)Department of Entomology, National Chung Hsing University, Taichung, Taiwan 
